ne, sustained watch time, ensuring that apparent scale does not outweigh real attention.\n\nIn aggregate, wexRAR+ provides a context-aware estimate of how much retention a creator is expected to generate relative to a replacement-level option, enabling more efficient, realistic, and impact-driven creator selection under real-world budgetary and operational constraints.\n\nImportant: wexRAR+ is not a standard formula; it has a base formula that we are collecting data on to improve its accuracy relating to its different modifiers, so please do not use that statistic as an end-all-be-all." + dynamicNote
